high_descs: Turn right and walk to the stove then turn left and walk to the wall then turn left.
Pick up the egg that's in front of you to the right of the sponge.
Turn left and take a step then turn left to face the fridge.
Chill the egg in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the sink that's in front of you and slightly to the right.
Open the microwave and put the egg in there then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold egg in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the right side of the white table
Grab the egg off of the table
Turn left and stop at the fridge
Cool the egg in the fridge and then take it out
Turn right and go to the microwave
Put the egg in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Putting a cooled egg in the microwave

high_descs: Turn right, then left and face the table to your left.
Take the potato off the table in front of you.
Turn left and face the fridge to your left.
Place the potato in the fridge, take out the potato and close the fridge.
Turn right and face the sink in front of you.
Place the potato in the microwave on top of the sink in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold potato in the microwave.
